00:33:04.730 --> 00:33:09.800
And here we have the results
of image recognition.

00:33:09.800 --> 00:33:14.010
And what I'm going to
do is read the word list

00:33:14.010 --> 00:33:19.510
that is contained here, and see
if we can get anything from this.

00:33:19.510 --> 00:33:22.720
So if we strung all these words
together, we would get image

00:33:22.720 --> 00:33:27.610
of joy, sorrow, anger, surprise,
exposed, blurred, headwear.

00:33:27.610 --> 00:33:29.910
And there's a 62%
confidence rating.

00:33:29.910 --> 00:33:33.050
So I think a lot of emotion
attached to this image,

00:33:33.050 --> 00:33:36.470
and that's why maybe there was
some difficulty with identifying

00:33:36.470 --> 00:33:37.470
what's there.

00:33:38.150 --> 00:33:40.170
This person does have a
