00:46:45.410 --> 00:46:53.410
Anonymous asks: Is there a gap
of describing images, by the way?

00:46:58.690 --> 00:47:02.600
What a seeing person sees
and what a blind person sees

00:47:02.600 --> 00:47:07.760
in the alt text that a seeing person
could miss telling in alt text,

00:47:07.760 --> 00:47:12.120
